1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,520
Si vivís

2
00:00:00,520 --> 00:00:01,080
en Valencia,

3
00:00:01,080 --> 00:00:02,160
tenéis que ver esto.

4
00:00:02,160 --> 00:00:02,920
Una mesa negra,

5
00:00:02,920 --> 00:00:03,960
tirada en Exposición,

6
00:00:03,960 --> 00:00:04,920
como si nada.

7
00:00:04,920 --> 00:00:05,560
Quedaos

8
00:00:05,560 --> 00:00:06,080
porque esto

9
00:00:06,080 --> 00:00:07,120
os interesa.

10
00:00:07,120 --> 00:00:08,360
Alguien la dejó aquí.

11
00:00:08,360 --> 00:00:09,080
Alguien más allá

12
00:00:09,080 --> 00:00:09,720
la necesita.

13
00:00:09,720 --> 00:00:10,480
Y no se van

14
00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:11,280
a encontrar nunca.

15
00:00:11,280 --> 00:00:12,080
Esa es la historia

16
00:00:12,080 --> 00:00:12,320
de siempre.

17
00:00:12,320 --> 00:00:13,400
Cosas buenas

18
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:14,280
que se pierden

19
00:00:14,280 --> 00:00:15,680
porque la persona

20
00:00:15,680 --> 00:00:16,160
que las tiene

21
00:00:16,160 --> 00:00:16,680
y la persona

22
00:00:16,680 --> 00:00:17,320
que las quiere

23
00:00:17,320 --> 00:00:17,920
no saben

24
00:00:17,920 --> 00:00:19,120
la una de la otra.

25
00:00:19,120 --> 00:00:20,040
Yo ya voy preparado

26
00:00:20,040 --> 00:00:21,360
para estos momentos.

27
00:00:21,360 --> 00:00:22,000
Abro Givore,

28
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:22,320
le echo

29
00:00:22,320 --> 00:00:23,440
una foto rápida,

30
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:24,160
y lo dejo ahí.

31
00:00:24,160 --> 00:00:25,120
No me complico.

32
00:00:25,120 --> 00:00:26,000
En cinco minutos

33
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:26,920
alguien lo ha visto

34
00:00:26,920 --> 00:00:27,480
y me escribe

35
00:00:27,480 --> 00:00:28,320
diciendo que lo quiere.

36
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:29,400
Cinco minutos.

37
00:00:29,400 --> 00:00:29,840
De la acera

38
00:00:29,840 --> 00:00:30,720
al salón de alguien

39
00:00:30,720 --> 00:00:32,240
que lo andaba buscando.

40
00:00:32,240 --> 00:00:32,600
Lo bonito

41
00:00:32,600 --> 00:00:33,880
es la conexión.

42
00:00:33,880 --> 00:00:34,600
Ni te conoces

43
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:35,040
ni te ves,

44
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:35,680
pero lo que a ti

45
00:00:35,680 --> 00:00:36,440
te sobraba

46
00:00:36,440 --> 00:00:37,440
a otro le ha cambiado

47
00:00:37,440 --> 00:00:37,760
el día.

48
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:38,600
¿Qué habéis encontrado

49
00:00:38,600 --> 00:00:39,200
vosotros

50
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:39,720
en la calle?

51
00:00:39,720 --> 00:00:40,680
Contádmelo,

52
00:00:40,680 --> 00:00:40,880
que quiero ver

53
00:00:40,880 --> 00:00:42,280
vuestros hallazgos.

